_sText:
Gg_alien

I made this map to try and create a station in space with an alien feel about it.
The map includes a lot of custom ambient sounds I have made in wavelab and also a custom skybox created by Karatekäfer. This is why the map size is almost 9mb, but its only about 3.5mb when zipped with bzip2.

maximum players:       36
recommended players: 20 - 30

Anyway hope you enjoy, please assess the map and tell me what you think.

Credits:

thanks to Karatekäfer for the skybox, and thanks to the many people who created some of these sounds which were later edited by me for this map.

elliotuk
